The package bundles third-party source code, enumerated below.  The vendored
tree under src/vendor/ is produced from pinned upstream releases by the
maintainer-run script tools/vendor.R; local modifications are limited to the
patches recorded in tools/patches/ (the replacement of std::cout/std::cerr
with R-safe output streams, and the removal of diagnostic-suppressing
compiler pragmas, both as required by CRAN policy for compiled code).  Exact
upstream versions and file hashes are recorded in tools/VENDOR_MANIFEST.


